Package:	lars
Version:	0.9-4
Date:		2003-05-16
Title:		Least Angle Regression, Lasso and Forward Stagewise
Author:		Trevor Hastie <hastie@stanford.edu> and Brad Efron 
		<brad@stat.stanford.edu>
Maintainer:	Trevor Hastie <hastie@stanford.edu>
